title: Fort Worth Mayor on Attracting New Residents and Businesses
itunes:title: Fort Worth Mayor on Attracting New Residents and Businesses
description:
Fort Worth, Texas Mayor Mattie Parker discusses how infrastructure improvements, educational opportunities and mobility are behind people moving to the North Texas area.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
